  USGS
  Minerals Information

                          Mineral Commodity Summaries

   Published on an annual basis, this report is the earliest Government
   publication to furnish estimates covering nonfuel mineral industry
   data. Data sheets contain information on the domestic industry
   structure, Government programs, tariffs, and 5-year salient statistics
   for over 90 individual minerals and materials.

   Availability: | WWW | FAX | CD-ROM | PRINTED COPIES |
